Vim: Scripts

Birkaç Vim Betiği

  • rails.vim: Ruby on Rails: easy file navigation, enhanced syntax highlighting, and more
  • Ruby Snippets: Some abbreviations to use with Ruby.
  • bufexplorer: Easily switch between buffers without knowing their numbers]]
  • winmanager: A windows style IDE for Vim 6.0
  • closetag: HTML ve XML dosyalarinda tag'lerin "CTRL+-" ile kapatilmasini saglar.
  • xmledit: A filetype plugin to help edit XML, HTML, and SGML documents
  • matchit: extended % matching for HTML, LaTeX?, and many other languages
